longBusinessSummary: A Metaverse Company, an investment holding company, engages in the media and metaverse business in the People's Republic of China. The company is involved in the licensing of drama series and films; the production of drama series and films, as well as distribution and related services; and provision of cloud gaming, software development, technology consulting services, and digital content production services. The company was formerly known as Starrise Media Holdings Limited and changed its name to A Metaverse Company in March 2022. A Metaverse Company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Wan Chai, Hong Kong.
